#: ../../source/unit/rfid.rst:3 923b084a804e4bcca6474399a21ceef0
msgid "RFID Unit"
msgstr "RFID Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/rfid.rst:7 d9755b1aab404f02a54b47006ea3384d
msgid ""
"RFIDUnit is a hardware module designed for RFID card reading and writing "
"operations. It extends the MFRC522 driver, supporting card detection, "
"reading, writing, and advanced features like selecting and waking up RFID"
" cards."
msgstr ""
"RFIDUnit 是一款用于 RFID 卡读写操作的硬件模块。它扩展了 MFRC522 驱动，支持卡片检测、读取、写入，以及选择和唤醒 RFID "
"卡等高级功能。"

